    <text>
        <body>
            <div>
                <opener><salute>D<hi rend="superscript">r</hi> Sir</salute></opener>
                <p>Hasty thanks are due for <persName ref="pe0214">M<hi rend="superscript">r</hi>
                        Williams</persName>
                    <bibl type="authorial"><title ref="bi0235">ingenious Essay</title></bibl>. My
                    thanks also to him for one in q<hi rend="superscript">to</hi> I had by <persName ref="pe0226">M<hi rend="superscript">r</hi> Panton</persName>.</p>
                <p>I am sorry for <persName ref="pe0006">Baileyâ€™s</persName> negligence: but really cannot
                    help it. He is a most remiss man; &amp; I often regretted the employing him.</p>
                <p>I beg my best wishes to <persName ref="pe0156">M<hi rend="superscript">r</hi>
                    Low</persName>. I beg to have his <bibl type="authorial"><title ref="bi0058">M.S.S</title></bibl>: if ready, &amp; fair by means of <persName ref="pe0026">M<hi rend="superscript">r</hi> White</persName>. perhaps he may get a
                    scribe in y<hi rend="superscript">r</hi> city. I hope he is concise for that is
                    what the public admire. I long for <rs ref="ar0204">his drawings</rs> which <persName ref="pe0014">my
                        Servant</persName> shall finish this winter. I need not recommend a safe
                    conveyance to <persName ref="pe0026">M<hi rend="superscript">r</hi>
                    White</persName>.</p>
                <closer><salute>I <lb/>am Dear Sir <lb/>Y<hi rend="superscript">r</hi> affect humble
                            Serv<hi rend="superscript">t</hi></salute>
                    <signed><persName ref="pe0232">Tho. Pennant</persName></signed>
                <dateline><placeName ref="pl0001">Downing</placeName> Aug. 8<hi rend="superscript">th</hi>
                    1777.</dateline></closer>
            </div>
            <div>
                <p><address>
                        <addrLine>M<hi rend="superscript">r</hi> Paton,</addrLine>
                        <addrLine>Custom house</addrLine>
                        <addrLine>Edinburgh</addrLine>
                    </address></p>
            </div>
        </body>
